Gold Price in Hong Kong Up
HONG KONG , November 30 ( Xinhua ) -- The gold price in Hong Kong rose one HK dollar to close at 2,728 HK dollars a tael on Monday , according to Po Sang Bank , one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong .
The gold price is equivalent to 295.74 U.S. dollars a troy ounce , 0.07 U.S. dollars up from the previous close at Monday 's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.743 HK dollars .
